        "URL": "data:text/html;charset=utf-8,%3C!doctype%20html%3E%0A%3Chtml%20lang%3D%22%22%3E%0A%3Chead%3E%0A%20%20%3Cmeta%20charset%3D%22utf-8%22%3E%0A%20%20%3Ctitle%3EMILK%3A%20What's%20that%20logo%2C%20anyway%3F%3C%2Ftitle%3E%0A%3C%2Fhead%3E%0A%3Cbody%3E%0A%3Cbody%3E%0A%0A%3Ctable%20class%3D%22milk-header%22%3E%0A%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%0A%20%20%3Ctd%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%22milk.com%20icon%22%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%20%20%3Ctd%3E%3Ch1%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22milk%22%3EMilk%3C%2Fspan%3E%3A%20What's%20that%20logo%2C%20anyway%3F%3C%2Fh1%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%3C%2Ftr%3E%0A%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%0A%0A%3Ch2%3EThe%20Short%20Answer%3C%2Fh2%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20stylized%20milk%20carton%2C%20with%20a%20picture%20of%20Kokopelli%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Ch2%3EThe%20Long%20Answer%3C%2Fh2%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20stylized%20milk%20carton%2C%20with%20a%20picture%20of%20Kokopelli%20on%20it.%20I%20think%0Athe%20milk%20carton%2F%22%3Cspan%20class%3D%22milk%22%3EMilk%3C%2Fspan%3E%22%20connection%20is%20pretty%0Aobvious%2C%20but%20what%20about%20Kokopelli%3F%20Well%2C%20in%20fact%0A%3Cspan%20class%3D%22milk%22%3EMilk%3C%2Fspan%3E%20stands%20for%20%22My%20Ittybitty%20Little%20Kokopelli.%22%0AThere%20you%20have%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Ch3%3ESo%2C%20who%20or%20what%20is%20this%20Kokopelli%20character%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3EKokopelli%20is%20a%20figure%20from%20Native%20American%20mythology%20(mainly%20from%0Athe%20southwest%20United%20States%20area).%20He's%20known%20as%0A%22the%20hunchback%20flute%20player%22%20and%20also%20as%20a%20general%20trickster.%20He's%0Aa%20god%20of%20abundance.%20Apparently%20there%20was%20a%20historical%20Kokopelli%20who%0Atraded%20grain%20seed%20for%2C%20uh%2C%20abundance%2C%20if%20you%20know%20what%20I%20mean.%20Suffice%0Ait%20to%20say%20that%2C%20if%20the%20legend%20is%20to%20believed%2C%20wherever%20Kokopelli%20went%2C%0Ahe%20left%20behind%20him%20a%20trail%20of%20fertile%20fields%20and%20pregnant%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Ch3%3EWhy%20do%20you%20like%20Kokopelli%20so%20much%3F%20%22Bornstein%22%20isn't%20exactly%20the%0Aname%20for%20a%20Nice%20Native%20American%20Boy!%3C%2Fh3%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20big%20fan%20of%20nifty%20abstract%20drawings%2C%20and%20the%20traditional%0AKokopelli-shape%20fits%20the%20bill%20in%20that%20department.%20I%20also%20think%20the%0Ahistorical%20Kokopelli%20had%20quite%20the%20scam%20going.%20What's%20more%2C%20my%0Abrother%20and%20(now%20ex-)%20sister-in-law%0Agave%20me%20a%20little%20wooden%20box%20with%20Kokopelli%20for%20my%20birthday%20a%20number%20of%0Ayears%20ago.%20So%2C%20I'm%20into%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Ch3%3EOk%2C%20enough%20with%20Kokopelli.%20What's%20with%20you%20and%20milk%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3EI%20like%20chocolate%20milk.%20I%20like%20coffee%20milk%20(it's%20a%20Rhode%20Island%20thing).%0AI%20like%20these%20things%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22%2Frecipes%2Fdrink%2Fitalian-cream.html%22%3E%22Italian%20Creams%22%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%0Asome%20cafes%20make.%20I%20like%20things%20that%20have%0Acondensed%20milk%20in%20them%20or%20that%20are%20made%20entirely%20from%20condensed%20milk%0A(i.e.%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22%2Frecipes%2Fdessert%2Fdulce-de-leche.html%22%3E%3Ci%3Edulce%20de%0Aleche%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E).%20(As%20my%20friend%0AGordie%20says)%20I'm%20Milk%20Boy%2C%20so%20how%20could%20I%20not%20have%20a%20site%20name%0Athat%20mentioned%20it%20at%20least%20obliquely%3F%20Ergo%2C%20%3Ccode%3Emilk.com%3C%2Fcode%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Ch3%3EAh%2C%20now%20I%20understand%2C%20but%20what%20does%20the%20logo%20%3Ci%3Emean%3C%2Fi%3E%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20while%20one%20of%20the%20places%20where%20one%20would%20see%20%22missing%20children%0Areports%22%20was%20on%20milk%20cartons%2C%20the%20theory%20being%20that%20this%20was%20an%20easy%0Away%20to%20reach%20lots%20of%20people%20and%20it%20was%20a%20good%20cause%2C%20etc.%20(I%20haven't%0Aseen%20this%20in%20a%20while%2C%20but%20perhaps%20some%20milk%20cartons%20still%20have%0Athem.%20Whatever.)%20So%2C%20the%20obvious%20conclusion%20is%20that%20Kokopelli%20is%0Amissing.%20The%20%3Cfont%20size%3D%22-1%22%3EFBI%3C%2Ffont%3E%2C%20or%20maybe%20his%20parents%2C%0Awill%20surely%20reward%20you%20if%20you%20have%20information%20leading%20to%20his%20safe%0Areturn.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3E(Thanks%20to%20my%20friend%20Ken%20for%20suggesting%20the%20meaning.)%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20way%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22whatsitnot.html%22%3Ethese%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20some%20things%0Athat%20the%20logo%20%3Ci%3Eisn't%3C%2Fi%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Ctable%20class%3D%22footer%22%3E%0A%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%0A%20%20%3Ctd%3ESite%20copyright%20%C2%A9%201994%E2%80%932024%20Dan%20Bornstein.%20All%20rights%20reserved.%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%20%20%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22%2F%22%3Emilk.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20%2F%20whatsit%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%3C%2Ftr%3E%0A%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%0A%0A%0A%0A%3C%2Fbody%3E%0A%3C%2Fbody%3E%0A%3C%2Fhtml%3E"
